  <summary date="2019-06-05T19:16:18Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Huntington's Disease Parity Act of 2019

This bill waives, for individuals diagnosed with Huntington's Disease, the 24-month waiting period for Medicare coverage.&#160;Current law generally applies this waiting period&#160;to individuals deemed eligible for Old-Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance benefits.</summary>
